channel.title: RSPS - A whole new world
channel.description:
[center][size=15pt]Welcome[/size] [size=8pt][i]RSPS - A whole new world.[/i][/size]
Welcome to a topic that most likely will blow your mind apart. I've decide to look back since RuneScape first began, remember it's not always about the improvements. While thinking back in the past I wondered, how did Jagex create the world '[i]RuneScape[/i]'. I decided to make a refractored client and remake RuneScape. I've expanded the RuneScape world by 10,000 more square tiles. I've removed the membership side of RuneScape and are thinking of remaking the whole membership side of RuneScape accept on the right side of the RuneScape world.
[b]Progress of Development:[/b] [i]25%[/i].
New Island Coordinates: 16789,11018.
[b][i](Pictures will be uploaded within development)[/i][/b]
